{
  "stem": "1753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 120.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he looks at it, and then this guy that paid me up, that paid me for the merchandise that I delivered to him, he probably didn't even understand.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He asked him, 'Is he a Jew?' He probably didn't even know what he said.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All he knew was one word, is [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says no, he knew I wasn't trouble.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, 'No.' So he said, 'Oh, so-- so how come you say?' I said, 'Look, I speak German, I feel like a German.' And that's how I saved.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in my pocket, I had the armband, the Jewish armband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So these are major or minor episodes which you experience day after day after day in a period of five some odd years.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So tell me more chutzpah stories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right now, they'll come some-- later on, there'll be some chutzpah stories.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in any case, so now we're in Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the railway terminated in the sand pit, and that was the dead end, literally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dead end.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just so one would understand, when I mention Treblinka, there were two Treblinkas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a Treblinka I, and there was a Treblinka II.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Treblinka I was the penal camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] prisoners from Treblinka I, in fact, built Treblinka II.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in order to get to Treblinka I, you have to pass Treblinka II first, ironically.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that morning, of course we didn't know, because the cattle cars were closed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when we arrived, I would say maybe 30% of that full transport of about 4,000 people probably died in transit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Never survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In any case, a good, good share of the people that ended the rail, the cattle cars in Rembertow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because of the lack of water and food.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
